{
  "texts": [
    "Put six wooden matches on the table or desk before you, as shown on the next page.",
    "Make an equilateral triangle from three of them.",
    "Use the remaining three matches to complete three more triangles, for a total of four.",
    "Each side of each triangle is to be the full length of a match.",
    "146 Basically, the task consists in creating three equilateral triangles from just six matches as depicted in Figure 1."
  ]
}